details.text: Constraint failed: eld-18: 'Must have a modifier reason if isModifier = true'
When HL7 is publishing a resource, the owning committee must be stated using the http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/structuredefinition-wg extension
Profile http://hl7.org/fhir/3.0/StructureDefinition/extension-Patient.animal is for a modifier extension, but the Patient.extension element is not a modifier
